<P>
The gay president of the Fremont school board is facing a recall drive. The 
Fremont Family Alliance won Alameda County approval to circulate petitions and 
has until Jan. 10 to collect the signatures of at least 12,219 of Fremont's 
81,495 registered voters in an effort to recall Robert Stipicevich. The 
