<HEADLINE>
<P>
NEWSWIRE: NAMES IN THE NEWS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Greg Lesher of Lebanon, Pa., will replace Allen Doyle of Atlanta on the United 
States team competing in the 32nd Walker Cup this week at Peachtree Golf Club 
in Atlanta. Doyle, five-time Georgia state amateur champion, withdrew because 
of a ruptured disk in his back. 
</P>
</TEXT>
