<HEADLINE>
<P>
NEWSWIRE: NAMES IN THE NEWS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Struggling pitcher Don August was sent to the minor leagues by the Milwaukee 
Brewers, who called up Jeff Peterek. August, 13-7 with a 3.09 earned-run 
average last season, is 9-11 with a 5.49 ERA. 
</P>
</TEXT>
<TYPE>
<P>
