</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
TWA Lowers Fares: TWA announced savings of up to $160 off its lowest fares to 
attract passengers to the fall and 1990 travel seasons. The company's "lowest 
fare guarantee" ensures that even if TWA's fares are reduced after tickets are 
purchased, passengers will be refunded the difference, and they will be allowed 
one "free" travel date change without penalty. Tickets can be purchased any 
time before Sept. 1 and from Sept. 9 through Dec. 15 for domestic travel, and 
for international travel from Oct. 1 through May 21, 1990. 
</P>
